cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with video generation using deep learning models, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The authors propose a new formulation of the problem using a Markov Decision Process (MDP), which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and reinforcement learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the generated videos using various metrics, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
